    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one and it still looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! No scratches, no dents, and the interior is still sparkling. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
