    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This example features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS to achieve a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including documented rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory-correct kinematics with fresh bushings and dampers, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in and chassis composure. A turn-key specimen for the collector demanding mechanical and aesthetic purity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
