    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it\u2019s been kept in tip-top shape inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for its next adventure, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
