    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a mechanically superlative specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This example is structurally flawless, with a verified reinforced subframe and a proactive rod bearing replacement already completed. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise engagement, channeling power through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension remains tight with original bushings in excellent health, and the chassis exhibits no signs of fatigue or oxidation. Finished in pristine Carbon Black with a factory-correct interior, this M3 retains its original staggered Style 67 alloys and cross-drilled rotors. A turn-key investment for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
